snippet.textDisplay: There are a couple items that I have that I feel are under rated or that I would like to see you review. I am actually subscribed to IPSY and received these items in my glam bag and was amazed by them. The first one is an eyeliner by Tart named sex kitten. It is the first liner that I have fallen in love with in a long time. I normally have a problem with any type of liquid liner causing irritation to my eyes and have had no problem with this one and it dries down amazing and stays even while I'm at work, and I have a very physical job. The second one is by Jules Smith beauty. It is a lip gloss or liquid lip I can't remember for sure, but the one I received was in the shade moonbeam dream and I fell in love with it. Like you I don't like a sticky feeling on my lips and have not had an issue with that, and also think that it is very hydrating for the lips. .... Maybe you would even be interested in doing a video where you try on products that your viewers suggest? Just an idea. Hope you take these two products into consideration.
